<section id="home" class="hero-area">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-12 col-12">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1 class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay=".4s">A powerful app to arrange your day.</h1>
          <p class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay=".6s">Revamp your task management with Taskbud. There’s never been a better time to be organized. Download Taskbud now!</p>
          <div class="button wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay=".8s">
            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jacknkiarie.taskbud" class="btn btn-alt"><i class="lni lni-play-store"></i> Google
              Play</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-12">
        <div class="hero-image wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay=".4s">
          <%= image_tag 'app_splash.png', width: '600', height: '800', alt: '#' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<section id="features" class="features section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h3 class="wow zoomIn" data-wow-delay=".2s">Features</h3>
          <h2 class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".4s">Your Experience Gets Better And Better Over Time.
          </h2>
          <p class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".6s">Don't take our word for it. TaskBud’s got unique and cool features that are going to turn the tide on your everyday grind in a blink.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">

        <div class="single-feature wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".2s">
          <i class="lni lni-cloud-upload"></i>
          <h3>Task Creation</h3>
          <p>Create tasks with ease, just type and hit the done button!</p>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">

        <div class="single-feature wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".4s">
          <i class="lni lni-alarm"></i>
          <h3>Notification Reminders</h3>
          <p>Go beyond a simple task list. Never forget a task again with timely reminders.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">

        <div class="single-feature wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".6s">
          <i class="lni lni-reload"></i>
          <h3>Task Completion</h3>
          <p>Mark your tasks as completed and watch them cross-out through the day, it‘s your victory!</p>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">

        <div class="single-feature wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".2s">
          <i class="lni lni-shield"></i>
          <h3>Daily Calendar View</h3>
          <p>Get your day’s tasks at a glance, neat and organized.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">

        <div class="single-feature wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".4s">
          <i class="lni lni-cog"></i>
          <h3>Tasks Tracker</h3>
          <p>Let Taskbud keep track and help you visualize your to-do list through a monthly snapshot</p>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">

        <div class="single-feature wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".6s">
          <i class="lni lni-layers"></i>
          <h3>Offline Support</h3>
          <p>Create and complete your tasks and sync with the cloud when you get back online</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<section id="overview" class="app-info section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="info-one">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-12">

          <div class="info-text wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay=".3s">
            <div class="main-icon">
              <i class="lni lni-inbox"></i>
            </div>
            <h2>Daily snapshot</h2>
            <p>Whether you’re a CEO, a wizard of Hyperbolic Time Chamber, or a goldfish with memory issues, you’re bound to love Taskbud. This smart app collects your to-dos. No fuss. No confusion. A dash of fun, a pinch of efficiency, and a load of organization!</p>
            <div class="button">
              <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jacknkiarie.taskbud" class="btn">Get Started</a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-12">
          <div class="info-image wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay=".5s">
            <%= image_tag 'home.png', height: 600, alt: 'app home screen' %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-one style2">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-12">
          <div class="info-image wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay=".3s">
            <%= image_tag 'profile.png', height: 600, alt: 'app profile screen' %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-12">

          <div class="info-text wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay=".5s">
            <div class="main-icon">
              <i class="lni lni-layout"></i>
            </div>
            <h2>Monthly Overview</h2>
            <p>We get it, remembering one task is easy. Remembering twenty-three? Absolute chaos. Don’t you worry, Taskbud has got your back.</p>
            <div class="button">
              <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jacknkiarie.taskbud" class="btn">Get Started</a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


